2003 PROMOTIONS
Earlier today, the Phillies announced the 2003 promotional 
schedule, including the "Field of Memories" events, a year-
long tribute to Veterans Stadium's 33rd and final season. 

The 1970s (4/6) and 80s (6/20-22) will be saluted, along 
with the 1993 NL Champion team (7/19-20). There's also the 
final Home Opener on April 4 at 1:33 p.m. and a Final 
Innings Celebration, September 26-27-28.  

2003 Promotional Schedule >>
http://lists.mlb.com/u/51573/7327517
"Field of Memories" Events >>
http://lists.mlb.com/u/51574/7327517
Final Year at the Vet >>
http://lists.mlb.com/u/51575/7327517

