***********************************************************
CHARLIE MANUEL JOINS PHILLIES
Former Indians manager Charlie Manuel has joined the Phillies 
organization as Special Assistant to the General Manager. 
Manuel will attend both major and minor league spring 
training, while evaluating the hitters.

For more on this story and other team news, check out the 
latest Inside Pitch >>
http://lists.mlb.com/u/51578/7327517

***********************************************************
2003 WINTER TOUR
The Phillies are ready to kick of their 35th annual Winter 
Tour, January 15-23. The Tour will take Phillies players, 
coaches, broadcasters and alumni to several exciting stops 
in the Delaware Valley and surrounding areas. 

For more details, check out the Tour dates and locations >>
http://lists.mlb.com/u/51579/7327517

